## Complete Returns & Refunds Policy

### Return Eligibility
- Time Period: 14 days from date of receipt
- Condition Required: Unused, original condition and packaging
- Purchase Source: Must be purchased directly from SYSUM
- Excluded Items:
  * Items not purchased directly from SYSUM
  * Items returned after 14-day period
  * Items not in original condition or packaging
  * Gift cards
  * Personalised or customised items (unless faulty or incorrect)

### UK Return Process
1. Fill out returns form on website: {{ shop.url }}/pages/returns
2. Receive email with Royal Mail collection link
3. Schedule collection or print label for post office drop-off
4. Return item (FREE - no cost to customer)
5. Refund processed within 10 working days of receipt

### International Return Process
1. Fill out returns form on website: {{ shop.url }}/pages/returns
2. Receive email with return instructions
3. Customer arranges and pays for return shipping
4. Recommend tracked shipping service
5. Items remain customer responsibility until received by SYSUM
6. Refund processed within 10 working days of receipt

### Refund Details
- Refund Amount: Cost of items returned
- Postage Refund: Only if items are faulty
- Refund Method: Original payment method
- Processing Time: Initiated within 10 working days
- Bank Processing: May take additional time depending on bank

### Exchange Process
- Availability: Subject to stock availability
- Request Method: Note desired exchange item in returns form
- Processing: Exchange sent once return received and inspected
- International: Customer covers return shipping, SYSUM covers exchange shipping

### Cancellation Before Dispatch
