### How to Measure Your Body

Chest / Bust:
Measure around your body underneath your armpits keeping the tape measure horizontal.

Waist:
Measure around your waist just above the hips, close to your belly button keeping the tape measure horizontal.

Hips:
Measure around the fullest part of your hips keeping the tape measure horizontal.

### Sizing Guidance
- Standard: UK and US sizing standards
- Between Sizes: We recommend selecting the larger size
- Wool Garments: Especially important to size up if between sizes
- Fit Information: Available in Size & Fit section of each product page
- Model Information: Height and size worn provided on product pages
- Assistance: Contact us for sizing help at {{ shop.url }}/pages/contact

## Product Care Guidelines

### General Care Instructions
- Washing: Machine wash at 30°C
- Bleaching: Do not bleach
- Drying: Do not tumble dry
- Dry Cleaning: Do not dry clean
- Ironing: Iron inside out on low heat

### Recommended Best Practice
- Method: Hand wash when possible
- Drying: Hang dry
- Reason: Reduces microplastic release into oceans
- Environmental Impact: Extends garment life, reduces energy use

### Special Material Care
- Merino Wool: Wash less frequently (naturally odor-resistant)
- Cordura® Nylon: Durable but follow care instructions for longevity
- Recycled Polyester: Standard care, avoid high heat

